1
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:43,193
Xia Rui!

2
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,917
Where are you going?

3
00:01:46,997 --> 00:01:50,089
I am staying...
I am staying outside for two days.

4
00:01:50,550 --> 00:01:53,673
Staying outside? I just saw you.

5
00:01:56,151 --> 00:02:00,954
Oh, my goodness! Are you staying in
with that boyfriend of yours?

6
00:02:02,253 --> 00:02:06,083
My God, girl!
Do you want everyone to hear it?

7
00:02:06,828 --> 00:02:09,474
How about this?
You help me to keep this a secret.

8
00:02:09,554 --> 00:02:12,388
I will pay for all your milk
tea for this month. Okay?

9
00:02:13,187 --> 00:02:15,671
But, it's almost the end of the month.

10
00:02:17,547 --> 00:02:20,352
I will also pay for next month, alright?

11
00:02:21,409 --> 00:02:24,172
Now that's more like it!
I will help you carry your luggage.

12
00:02:25,224 --> 00:02:26,933
But, let me tell you.

13
00:02:27,233 --> 00:02:30,950
There are things you need be mindful of
when living together.

14
00:02:31,761 --> 00:02:34,320
I read an online comment
from someone saying that...

15
00:02:34,410 --> 00:02:37,850
staying together is one of the reasons
why couples break up.

16
00:02:37,930 --> 00:02:39,636
You better be careful.

17
00:02:39,716 --> 00:02:42,406
I treat you for milk tea
and you treat me like this?

18
00:02:42,486 --> 00:02:45,091
I am not cursing you.
I am worried about you.

19
00:02:45,171 --> 00:02:48,083
Also, what was his explanation
on the photos two days ago?

20
00:02:48,576 --> 00:02:49,977
I saw it with my eyes.

21
00:02:50,057 --> 00:02:54,406
You went crazy when you saw photos of him
dancing with other people.

22
00:02:54,790 --> 00:02:55,788
Yang Yufei?

23
00:02:55,869 --> 00:03:00,061
Oh, no. You misunderstood.
That's just a misunderstanding.

24
00:03:00,141 --> 00:03:01,439
-Slowly.
-Okay.

25
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,679
-Watch your hand.
-Alright.

26
00:03:07,522 --> 00:03:09,203
This is the last box.

27
00:03:10,529 --> 00:03:15,617
Did I bring too much stuff?

28
00:03:15,697 --> 00:03:17,668
How can it be? Not much.

29
00:03:17,748 --> 00:03:20,747
But, we need to move it upstairs later.

30
00:03:21,237 --> 00:03:23,364
Do you want to move it now or later?

31
00:03:23,945 --> 00:03:26,517
Let's move it now.

32
00:03:29,494 --> 00:03:30,436
But...

33
00:03:30,516 --> 00:03:33,788
