slip on the ones I see.

51
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:48,167
As for these books,
they are neatly put here.

52
00:04:48,247 --> 00:04:50,808
Look, grab one of it
and there's hospitality management.

53
00:04:50,888 --> 00:04:52,230
Isn't it convenient?

54
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:55,078
I hung up the clothes here
to prevent wrinkling.

55
00:04:55,158 --> 00:04:58,518
Over here are my beauty products.

56
00:04:59,506 --> 00:05:02,093
