57
00:05:04,174 --> 00:05:06,053
As long as you are comfortable,
then it's fine.

58
00:05:17,691 --> 00:05:20,465
Nan Xi, Nan Xi.

59
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:24,175
Boss Yi wants me to bring you along
to work tomorrow.

60
00:05:24,255 --> 00:05:26,207
I don't know what he is planning.

61
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,713
I will accompany you.

62
00:05:29,793 --> 00:05:32,376
