He wants to meet you.

63
00:05:35,313 --> 00:05:37,717
If I go there,
it's considered me accompanying you.

64
00:05:41,141 --> 00:05:42,265
Come over here.

65
00:05:43,243 --> 00:05:46,306
You are getting good at sweet talk lately.

66
00:05:46,386 --> 00:05:47,817
Who taught you this?

67
00:05:49,081 --> 00:05:50,829
Have you finished memorizing the text?

68
00:05:54,063 --> 00:05:56,393
I am going to memorize it now, Nan Xi.

69
00:06:13,461 --> 00:06:15,183
Nothing, nothing.

70
00:06:30,698 --> 00:06:33,306
I have helped you
settle the university forum issue.

71
00:06:33,386 --> 00:06:34,707
Had it not been for Boss Yi intervening,

72
00:06:34,787 --> 00:06:38,340
I would have blacklisted Yang Yufei.

73
00:06:38,906 --> 00:06:39,986
Yang Yufei?

74
00:06:40,066 --> 00:06:41,847
What does this have anything to do
with her?

75
00:06:41,927 --> 00:06:42,991
Why are you taking it out on her?

76
00:06:43,071 --> 00:06:44,672
Isn't she the one who uploaded the post?

77
00:06:45,452 --> 00:06:47,287
Of course, it isn't her.

78
00:06:47,367 --> 00:06:49,460
She is also a victim.

79
00:06:51,392 --> 00:06:54,267
If she didn't upload the photos,
then who did it?

80
00:06:54,347 --> 00:06:57,627
It was her classmates,
who like spreading baseless rumors.

81
00:06:57,718 --> 00:07:01,954
When Yang Yufei was in school,
didn't she have a crush on Nan Xi?

82
00:07:03,259 --> 00:07:04,350
Yes, she did.

83
00:07:04,904 --> 00:07:08,685
But, Yang Yufei was not involved in it.

84
00:07:08,765 --> 00:07:12,654
Also, I was in that class too.

85
00:07:12,734 --> 00:07:14,083
You are spying on Nan Xi?

86
00:07:14,163 --> 00:07:15,676
How is this spying?

87
00:07:15,756 --> 00:07:17,240
This is considered as caring, okay?

88
00:07:17,696 --> 00:07:20,286
Moreover, Yang Yufei had contacted me,

89
00:07:20,366 --> 00:07:22,222
to tell me that she will help me
delete the post.

90
00:07:22,302 --> 00:07:24,502
The innocent need not do anything.

91
00:07:24,582 --> 00:07:27,207
Just letting it to is the best response.

92
00:07:27,287 --> 00:07:29,222
Didn't you have a crush on Yang Yufei?

93
00:07:29,302 --> 00:07:30,750
What happened all of a sudden?

94
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:33,395
I, Binzi, am a person with principles.

95
00:07:33,475 --> 00:07:35,192
I always focus on facts, not people.

96
00:07:35,272 --> 00:07:37,949
Let me tell you.
Be careful with your words.

97
00:07:38,029 --> 00:07:41,143
You might lose the people you love.

98
00:07:41,861 --> 00:07:42,976
Okay.

99
00:07:50,669 --> 00:07:53,199
Sorry to keep you waiting.

100
00:07:54,049 --> 00:07:55,411
Oh, my goodness.

101
00:07:55,491 --> 00:07:56,974
How is he so handsome?

102
00:07:58,020 --> 00:07:59,525
I want to add him on WeChat.

103
00:08:09,066 --> 00:08:10,648
I see what you did there, Boss Yi.

104
00:08:10,728 --> 00:08:12,394
Without him here,
your business wouldn't run.

105
00:08:12,474 --> 00:08:14,213
I was wondering why you asked Nan Xi
to come here.

106
00:08:14,293 --> 00:08:17,433
It's because you wanted him to be the
mascot to increase customer turnover.

107
00:08:17,513 --> 00:08:18,571
I disagree with that.

108
00:08:18,651 --> 00:08:21,691
