109
00:08:21,771 --> 00:08:22,805
Why?

110
00:08:22,885 --> 00:08:26,407
So that he can appreciate your charm
while you work.

111
00:08:26,487 --> 00:08:28,258
If you don't believe me,
ask him if he likes it or not.

112
00:08:28,338 --> 00:08:30,596
Nan Xi didn't even want to come here
to begin with.

113
00:08:30,676 --> 00:08:33,887
You really are a fox.
Good with words, too.

114
00:08:33,967 --> 00:08:35,248
You are misusing the idioms again.

115
00:08:35,328 --> 00:08:38,085
Why does your Nan Xi
have to be so attractive?

116
00:08:38,165 --> 00:08:39,262
Look at them.

117
00:08:39,342 --> 00:08:41,068
To show you my appreciation,

118
00:08:41,148 --> 00:08:44,962
I will teach you the core technique
of making coffee, okay?

119
00:08:45,614 --> 00:08:46,701
Deal!

120
00:08:50,535 --> 00:08:52,709
It's a rare opportunity
to see our boss perform.

121
00:08:52,789 --> 00:08:53,904
Is the camera focused?

122
00:08:53,984 --> 00:08:55,052
Yes, of course.

123
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:57,877
Let me see, let me see.

124
00:09:04,136 --> 00:09:05,220
What do you think?

125
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:06,722
Was it worth your tuition fees?

126
00:09:06,802 --> 00:09:08,908
Master, please accept me as your disciple.

127
00:09:08,988 --> 00:09:09,838
Stand up.

128
00:09:09,918 --> 00:09:12,531
Hurry up and deliver the coffee
to the customer.

129
00:09:12,611 --> 00:09:14,228
Wait, let me do a closeup. Put it here.

130
00:09:16,084 --> 00:09:18,552
