if customers complain?

144
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:46,158
No, no, no.

145
00:09:56,810 --> 00:09:58,192
Wow, if a person is handsome,

146
00:09:58,272 --> 00:10:00,303
he looks good in every photo,
no matter it was taken.

147
00:10:00,383 --> 00:10:02,239
Hey, what kind of photo is this?

148
00:10:02,319 --> 00:10:04,771
This angle doesn't do justice to his face.
You still think he looks good?

149
00:10:04,851 --> 00:10:06,387
He was just sitting down
while I took these.

150
00:10:06,467 --> 00:10:07,382
Why don't you try?

151
00:10:07,462 --> 00:10:09,538
Okay then, I will try. Go away.

152
00:10:09,618 --> 00:10:10,767
